    "instruction": "Final diagnosis summary (concise):\nRoot-cause component: rabbitmq (message broker).\nFailure reason: socket error (message-broker socket/connectivity issue causing widespread service errors).\nEvidence: persistent socket KPI anomalies on rabbitmq and many other services starting 2024-01-20T21:58:00Z; rabbitmq-exporter and queue-master also show continuous anomalies; widespread log.error_count > 0 across services beginning ~21:58Z. Suggested next actions: check RabbitMQ node health (network/socket limits, listeners, connection counts), inspect RabbitMQ logs for socket/connection errors, and if needed restart or scale the broker and reconnect queue-master/clients."  
}

